{"tid":2516013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"菲律賓外長洛欽：林鄭是鴉片戰爭以來，香港最好的領導人","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:18:46.000Z","uid":37112,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b01a5f3e4d5772376ed37251b5e0d1c80d1c1c","tid":2516013,"uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:11:21.000Z","msg":"菲律賓外長歡迎香港重新檢視要求外傭接種疫苗的要求<br />\n<br />\n對於行政長官林鄭月娥說，已經要求勞工及福利局重新檢視外傭新來港或續約時，必須接種新冠疫苗的要求，菲律賓外長洛欽表示歡迎。洛欽在社交網站貼文，形容林鄭月娥的反應迅速和明智，讚揚對方是鴉片戰爭以來，香港最好的領導人，對此表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n2021-05-04 18:50:47"},{"pid":"d80e471dc430d9db5c7c11c4c88d9f6fdfbfd57f","tid":2516013,"uid":105790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"以為老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea18192dd8afdcb89ffad2525673b4038c7c787b","tid":2516013,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"係咪仲未收到風班賓妹要比科興強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f5387c75575e7735e24c3292cdcca58325382b","tid":2516013,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea18192dd8afdcb89ffad2525673b4038c7c787b","tid":2516013,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"係咪仲未收到風班賓妹要比科興強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"對佢有影響咩?"},{"pid":"552b2843009d3452804a2fe89bfe4d2402db1d48","tid":2516013,"uid":63782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"分唔到曲線定直線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2898f4d87d15a94fe56d280414877f3e0b6db8","tid":2516013,"uid":100273,"like":0